40
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,160
In fact, these new eyes of mine

41
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,200
belonged to Master Yuan Gui.

42
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,000
So, what you saw just now

43
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,600
was the sheer truth.

44
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,680
That is to say,

45
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,640
elder Yuan Gui was already killed
when he was in Devil Sect.

46
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,400
Yuan Zhao

47
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,680
To cover up for your illegitimate son,

48
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,560
you signed us all up for dirty business.

49
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,440
