114
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:47,200
So, Hou Chi should give up
the seal of the head of the Alliance.

115
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:52,320
Then we will find someone truly qualified
to take the place.

116
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,440
I should be the only one to blame

117
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,880
for what happened today.

118
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,800
I have ruined the reputation
of the Immortal Sect.

119
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,880
