the title of the Yuhua Sect owner.

120
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,960
I am willing to give up my position

121
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,520
to make things just.

122
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:10,560
However,

123
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:14,640
all matters about the head of the Alliance
should refer to Shen Guan.

124
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,240
We have to report to Shen Guan,

125
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:18,000
and wait for her decision.

126
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,600
I believe Lord Shen Guan

127
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,760
will make the right decision.

128
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:40,120
I'm aware of what happened today.

129
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:44,640
Hou Chi's position as the head
was what meant to be.

130
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,040
It has nothing to do with sect conflicts.

131
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:51,440
So Hou Chi should still
be the head of Immortals Alliance.

132
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,360
I'll hear no further discussions.

133
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:54,720
Hou Chi

134
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,840
Report to the Celestial Palace
to take up your position tomorrow.

135
00:11:58,760 --> 00:11:59,760
Make no mistakes.

136
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:02,840
Yes.

137
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,840
I have sent my words back to Yuhua Sect.

138
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,920
The owner of the sect

139
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,560
will be Senior Yuan Ye.

140
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,880
From now on,

141
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,400
he will be in charge of

142
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,000
everything in Yuhua Sect.

143
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,000
Qing Feng and Yi Yaogua

144
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,360
After I leave,

145
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:30,760
the two of you

146
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,160
shall escort Hou Chi to the Celestial Palace

147
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,920
and help him take up his position.

148
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,880
Master, please allow me to quit Yuhua Sect.

149
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,240
Qing Feng

150
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,360
It was just Master's mad word

151
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,240
