152
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,240
Don't let it go to your head.

153
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:49,800
But I took them seriously.

154
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,400
Many things happened these days.

155
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,720
Some of them troubled me with confusion.

156
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:58,480
As for the conflict between the Immortals and Devils,
and the gap between right from wrong.

157
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,520
I was confused.

158
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,680
So from now on,

159
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,680
I just wish to go my own way,

160
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,720
and do my own deed.

161
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,760
Please allow me to quit Yuhua Sect.

162
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,000
In that case,

163
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,200
Master, please allow me

164
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,760
to follow Qing Feng.

165
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,000
I am not the owner anymore,

166
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,560
so I have no right to stop you.

167
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:37,760
You should

168
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,400
make this decision yourselves.

169
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,440
Master, I bid you farewell.

170
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,320
Master Hou Chi, I bid you farewell.

171
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,400
Master, I bid you farewell.

172
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,000
Master Hou Chi

173
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,040
Farewell.

174
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:11,520
Chi

175
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,600
Master

176
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,840
I must have

177
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,640
let you down.

178
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,480
As your disciple, I'm in no position

179
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,280
to judge your past.

180
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,840
But I have been following your words
ever since I was young.

181
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,600
I believe that

182
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:40,880
