half as bright as you are.

185
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,280
Senior is kind by nature.

186
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:55,880
He was seduced by that devil woman.

187
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:58,200
That's why he lost himself for the moment.

188
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,640
After I take up my position,

189
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,440
I will help you get him back.

190
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,200
If he is unwilling to return,

191
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,160
just let him be.

192
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,080
Every one of us had our own path written

193
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,520
when we were born.

194
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:22,800
And we must go down these paths

195
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,560
throughout our life.

196
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:28,760
Bi Hong

197
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:31,000
is destined to be a mortal.

198
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,720
And you are bound to have a high position,

199
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:40,040
and bring honor to Yuhua Sect.

200
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,000
It's your Succession Ceremony tomorrow.

201
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,400
I can't be publicly present,

202
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:51,120
but I'll be there in the shadows.

203
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:01,840
Chi

204
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:05,240
No matter what will happens tomorrow,

205
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,760
