224
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:15,920
But my family has got sufficient wealth.

225
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:17,840
Wherever you wish to be,

226
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,080
we can go and settle their together.

227
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,640
I don't want your money or houses.

228
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,840
That's not what I meant.

229
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:24,520
I...

230
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:26,840
I know you're not a fan of any of that.

231
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,600
I just want to make you a home.

232
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,240
A warm place for two.

233
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,560
Did I say something wrong again?

234
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,240
If you dare to kiss me
without consent again,

235
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,880
I will break your legs.

236
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:52,480
Alright.

237
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:53,920
I won't kiss you without your consent again.

238
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:55,320
Only you can kiss me at will.

239
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,040
So is that a yes?

240
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,680
We've got a long way ahead.

241
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,960
Where should we start?

242
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,720
I want to go to the bottom of the cliff

243
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,800
to find the bodies of Shi Xia and Shi Dong.

244
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:24,800
