250
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:50,880
Follow me.

251
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,280
Shi Xia, Devil Lord

252
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,440
Are they...

253
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:19,680
Shi Dong is fine.

254
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,560
They are just asleep.

255
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,600
So you have figured a way out for them
since the beginning.

256
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,840
Trapped by the Evil Aura,

257
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,600
I'm no longer that powerful.

258
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:43,640
If Shi Xia gets into trouble one day,

259
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:45,520
I might not be there in time.

260
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:50,680
I hope this ring

261
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:52,760
can protect Shi Xia for me.

262
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:11,240
I'll have to ask you for a favor.

263
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:14,080
Please hide them well
and take good care of them.

264
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:16,400
Please don't tell them what happened
while they're asleep.

265
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:18,720
And please don't tell them that

266
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,400
