267
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,680
Since you still love Shi Xia,

268
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,120
why don't you tell her the truth?

269
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:29,520
Yeah, why not?

270
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,440
Shi Xia loves you so.

271
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,400
You care for each other.

272
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,720
