Not only you are alive,

283
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:48,560
Devil Lord is alive, too.

284
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,480
He is right next door.

285
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,800
We fell that far,

286
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:54,360
and my brother was stabbed.

287
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:55,960
How did we manage to survive?

288
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:00,800
You and Devil Lord fell
to the bottom of the cliff.

289
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,000
I didn't want your bodies left in the wild,

290
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:05,960
so Yi Yaogua and I went to look for you.

291
00:22:06,520 --> 00:22:07,640
When we got there,

292
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:08,960
we found you lying there.

293
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,320
Thank goodness you were both alive.

294
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,040
Qing Feng

295
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:21,640
What would I do without you?

296
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,320
It's fine now.

297
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,840
Everything is over.

298
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,400
By the way,

299
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:32,280
everyone thinks you and Devil Lord are dead,

300
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:35,440
so you have to stay here and can't go anywhere

301
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,480
until they forget about this matter.

302
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,400
Okay.

303
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:43,400
Where exactly are we?

304
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:44,720
This is...

305
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:48,000
This is my house in the Otherworld Town,

306
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,280
but soon

307
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:53,000
it will also be Qing Feng's house.

308
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:58,800
What's going on with you guys?

309
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:01,400
Qing Feng and I are no longer

310
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,360
apprentices of Yuhua Sect.

311
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,240
She is the new owner of Qingcheng Sect,

312
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:07,480
while I am her fiancé.

313
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:09,440
All the houses of my family

314
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,280
will become the territory of Qingcheng Sect.

315
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,640
You guys made quite the progress

316
00:23:16,080 --> 00:23:17,760
while I was asleep.

317
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,120
When's the wedding?

318
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,600
Don't listen to him.

319
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,760
I haven't even said yes yet.

320
00:23:26,760 --> 00:23:27,880
I've prepared her dowry.

321
00:23:28,320 --> 00:23:29,320
It'll happen soon.

322
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,920
I want to see my brother, Shi Dong.

323
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,080
His room is across from yours.

324
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,520
Was it wrong to

325
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,520
hide it from her like this?

326
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:04,800
I think we should tell her the truth.

327
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:05,720
No.

328
00:24:06,520 --> 00:24:07,680
Things happened these days

329
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:08,440
are enough to prove

330
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:10,040
Yuan Zhao's determination to kill Shi Xia.

331
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:12,520
If we choose to tell her the truth now,

332
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:15,680
we would ruin Master Hou Chi's efforts.

333
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,200
Ow ow owie.

334
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,160
It hurts. Be gentle.

335
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,800
It was you who stabbed him first.

336
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:27,000
He only fought back.

337
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,240
My silly sister.

338
00:24:30,560 --> 00:24:31,640
He meant to kill me,

339
00:24:32,080 --> 00:24:33,120
and you are still on his side.

340
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,160
Quit mumbling.

341
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:38,960
The moment he decided to kill us,

342
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,200
my love for him was totally gone.

343
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,200
Since I have paid all that's due,

344
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:46,440
his life

345
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:48,240
matters to me no more.

346
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:53,480
Then why are you still wearing this ring

347
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,360
he gave you?

348
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,000
I just forgot to take it off.

349
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:07,240
Just throw it away for me.

350
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,400
Even when I sleep, it's harsh to my skin.

351
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:04,640
I put all the scenery in the yard

352
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,200
into this snow globe.

353
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,080
If you ever feel homesick,

354
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:09,480
just take a look at it.

355
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,440
What about you? Are you also in it?

356
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:17,680
Seasons may go by,

357
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,200
but in this snow globe

358
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:20,720
it's always summer.

359
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,720
(You said you liked trees,)

360
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:45,840
(so I made you a ring of leaves,)

361
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,800
(not sure if you like it.)

362
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,640
The liquor has already gone.

363
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:09,200
Never mind.

364
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:12,960
I have another pot.

365
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:28,520
Hou Chi

366
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,800
Why don't you trust me?

367
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,560
(Why she is drinking again?)

368
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,400
Even if you have taken
the Love-forgetting Potion,

369
00:27:40,080 --> 00:27:41,680
you should have believed in me.

370
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:45,960
Do I look like a bad guy?

371
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,520
The cliff was that high.

372
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,800
If I were not so lucky,

373
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:56,560
I would have died for good.

374
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,200
Hou Chi

375
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:30,800
You are the coldest, hardest

376
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:32,600
and the most stupid
piece of log in this world.

377
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,320
You know nothing about love.

378
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,040
Now listen up.

379
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,320
My next boyfriend

380
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:45,960
is sweet, gentle, and considerate.

381
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,800
He's taller and finer than you, too.

382
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:53,280
I will get myself a boyfriend here,

383
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,480
and I'll get another one as I go home.

384
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,600
Just wait and see.

385
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,760
However merciless you are to me,

386
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:26,240
I can't forget your love on my part.

387
00:29:30,120 --> 00:29:31,480
Even without me,

388
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:36,160
you are still the brightest star
in the night sky.

389
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:43,760
Tomorrow
you'll enjoy the highlight of your life.

390
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:48,080
I hope whatever the Celestial Seal foretold

391
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,400
never comes true.

392
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:49,040
What you miss at day

393
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:51,120
what you dream at night.

394
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,360
It feels just like the real thing.

395
00:31:03,800 --> 00:31:06,840
The liquor of the rich sure is something.

396
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:10,160
(Is she sleepwalking?)

397
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:13,920
Shi Xia

398
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:17,440
He can even talk.

399
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,840
(If she wakes up in shock,)

400
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,320
(this will be hard to explain.)

401
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,280
I won't let you get away

402
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:26,640
in my own dream.

403
00:31:29,360 --> 00:31:30,120
It's just a dream after all.

404
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,760
I can do whatever I want.

